name: into the dark
description:
This photograph was taken in the recesses of Madera Canyon, some time around dusk. Light is not absent from the foreboding scene - what's left of it works to highlight a textural nuance in the landscape. These patterns present a codified flow to the viewer, guiding perceptually and imaginatively.


Location: Madera Canyon, Santa Cruz, Arizona
Artist: Sean Thayer
IG and Twitter: @abstrctogrphy
